import React from 'react';
import {
  LoginFormContainer,
  LoginForm,
  InputLabel,
  LoginInput,
  LoginIcon,
  LoginErrorMessageContainer,
  ErrorMessage
} from './style'

import UserIcon from '../../assets/images/userLoginImage.png'
import PasswordIcon from '../../assets/images/passwordLoginImage.png';

const LoginFormComponent = ({teste}) => {
  return (
    <LoginFormContainer>
      <LoginForm onSubmit={console.log('testei o envio')}>
        <InputLabel>
          <LoginInput type='text' name='userInput' placeholder='UsuÃ¡rio'/>
          <LoginIcon src={UserIcon} alt='User Icon'/>
        </InputLabel>
        <InputLabel>
          <LoginInput type='password' name='passwordInput' placeholder='Senha'/>
          <LoginIcon src={PasswordIcon} alt='Password Icon'/>
        </InputLabel>
      </LoginForm>
      <LoginErrorMessageContainer>
        <ErrorMessage id='error-message'>teste1</ErrorMessage>
        <ErrorMessage id='error-message'>teste2</ErrorMessage>
      </LoginErrorMessageContainer>
    </LoginFormContainer>
  )
}

export default LoginFormComponent;
